  "stem": "<p>The table summarizes the distribution of color and shape for 200 buttons of equal size.</p><figure class=\"table\"><table border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th></th><th>Yellow</th><th>Green</th><th>Total</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Circle</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">50</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">30</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">80</td></tr><tr><td>Square</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">40</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">80</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">120</td></tr><tr><td>Total</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">90</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">110</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">200</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>If one of these buttons is selected at random, what is the probability that the button is yellow and square? (Express your answer as a decimal or fraction, not as a percent.)</p>",
